s surgeries.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dr. Anushree Kaduskar-Aney</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\nShe has completed her DNB and long-term fellowship in paediatric ophthalmology from Sankara Nethralaya Chennai, and is a consultant in this department.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dr. Sudhir Taras</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\nHe is a formally trained paediatric orthoptist, and has received training at the Aravind Eye Hospital, Madurai. He is a devoted member of the team, and is highly dedicated to the treatment of eye problems in children, especially strabismus.</p>'),(2233,371,'_page_content','field_5cee199f0b963'),(2234,372,'_edit_lock','1560421678:1'),(2235,375,'_edit_lock','1560419516:1'),(2236,377,'_edit_lock','1560419498:1'),(2237,380,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2238,380,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','311'),(2239,380,'_menu_item_object_id','377'),(2240,380,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2241,380,'_menu_item_target',''),(2242,380,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2243,380,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2244,380,'_menu_item_url',''),(2246,381,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2247,381,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','311'),(2248,381,'_menu_item_object_id','375'),(2249,381,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2250,381,'_menu_item_target',''),(2251,381,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2252,381,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2253,381,'_menu_item_url',''),(2255,382,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2256,382,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','311'),(2257,382,'_menu_item_object_id','372'),(2258,382,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2259,382,'_menu_item_target',''),(2260,382,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2261,382,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2262,382,'_menu_item_url',''),(2264,383,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2265,383,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','47'),(2266,383,'_menu_item_object_id','377'),(2267,383,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2268,383,'_menu_item_target',''),(2269,383,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2270,383,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2271,383,'_menu_item_url',''),(2273,384,'_menu_item_typ