ed queries and for fixing an appointment for consultation, <a href=\"/contact/\">contact H.V. Desai Hospital </a></p>\r\n\r\n					\r\n\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div> <!-- accordion end -->\r\n\r\n			\r\n			\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),(2293,264,'_page_content','field_5cee199f0b963'),(2294,339,'page_content',''),(2295,339,'_page_content','field_5cee199f0b963'),(2296,386,'home_image',''),(2297,386,'_home_image','field_5cd00574bd707'),(2298,386,'page_content',''),(2299,386,'_page_content','field_5cee199f0b963'),(2300,387,'home-image',''),(2301,387,'_home-image','field_5cc174cd08a80'),(2302,387,'state_of_art_image','158'),(2303,387,'_state_of_art_image','field_5cc174cd08a80'),(2304,387,'state_of_art_title','State-of-the-art Facilities'),(2305,387,'_state_of_art_title','field_5cc17ef31ddc2'),(2306,387,'state_of_art_description','<p>PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital has all the latest equipment, which includes an ND:YAG laser machine, B Scan facility, Pentacam, Phaco machine, portable vitrectomy facility, Lumenis multisport laser machine, and a Mobile Eye Care van facility, to provide the highest quality of services to patients. In addition, it has a team of highly experienced specialists with years of experience. What’s more, the hospital’s skills & training centre ensures that its in-house doctors are updated with all the latest techniques and knowledge related to their field. \r\n</p><div class=\"learn-more-wrapper\"><button class=\"learn-more\">Learn More</button></div>'),(2307,387,'_state_of_art_description','field_5cc1803f1ddc3'),(2308,387,'pioneer_img_1','159'),(2309,387,'_pioneer_img_1','field_5ccc399e2f48c'),(2310,387,'pioneer_name_1','Late Mr. Tukaram Bamankar'),(2311,387,'_pioneer_name_1','field_5ccc3a062f48d'),(2312,387,'pioneer_link_1','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"Learn\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(2313,387,'_pioneer_link_1','field_5ccc3a172f48e'),(2314,387,'pioneer_img_2','79'),(2315,387,'_pioneer_img_2','field_5ccc3abea352f'),(2316