.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:282;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(3638,813,'_wp_attached_file','2019/07/Ped.Opthalmology.png'),(3639,813,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:670;s:6:\"height\";i:630;s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"2019/07/Ped.Opthalmology.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"Ped.Opthalmology-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"Ped.Opthalmology-300x282.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:282;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(3640,814,'home_image','165'),(3641,814,'_home_image','field_5cd00574bd707'),(3642,814,'page_content','<div class=\"common-wrapper clear-both\">\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n			<div class=\"accordion active\">\r\n				<div class=\"accordion-title\">Paediatric Ophthalmology and Squint Department <span class=\"float-right\">+</span></div>\r\n				<div class=\"accordion-desc\">\r\n\r\n<p>The paediatric ophthalmology services offered at H. V. Desai Eye Hospital are dedicated to provide comprehensive ophthalmic care to children aged below 16 years. The provision of these services is aimed at ensuring that no child is becomes blind, and to provide equal rights to children suffering from low vision as well as increased accessibility to all the possible medical services to enable them to play an active role in society. The paediatric ophthalmology services offered at the hospital provide treatment for all types vision-related problems in children, some of which are listed below:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Refractive error</li>\r\n 	<li>Amblyopia (Lazy eye)</li>\r\n 	<li>Paediatric cataract</li>\r\n 	<li>Paediatric squint</li>\r\n 	<li>Nystagmus</li>\r\n 	<li>Low vision</li>\r\n 	<li>Ocular trauma</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\nIn addition to the above-mentioned issues, the paediatric ophthalmology department, in collaboration with the retina department, takes an active part in screening and visually rehabilitating kids suffering from Retinopathy of Prematurity (ROP).\r\n</p><p>\r\nWith the glaucoma and oculoplasty department, common childhood problems such as paediatric glaucoma and oculoplasty disorders (nasolacrimal duct obstruction, ptosis, entropion, blepharophimosis, etc.) are also treated here. In addition, the strabismology services offered by this department provide treatment to adult patients suffering from double vision and squint.\r\n</p><p>\r\nThis department examines and treats around 10,000 patients each year, which include the surgical treatment of around 2,500 children per year.\r\n</p><p>\r\nThis department is also actively involved in school screening in the Pune and Satara districts to help in the earliest possible detection of ophthalmic conditions among children. This community outreach program helps paediatric patients to receive the best possible ophthalmic care at the earliest.\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"accordion\">\r\n				<div class=\"accordion-title\">Education and Training\r\n\r\n<span class=\"float-right\">+</span></div>\r\n				<div class=\"accordion-desc\">\r\n<p>This department also has a structured fellowship program in paediatric ophthalmology and strabismus, which are listed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Short-term fellowship (3 months)</li>\r\n 	<li>Long-term fellowship(ORBIS supported) (15 months)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(3643,814,'_page_content','field_5cee199f0b963'),(3644,817,'page_description','<p>Comprehensive <strong>quality eye</strong><br /><strong>care</strong> with equity</p>'),(3645,817,'_page_description','field_5cdd0e073df07'),(3646,817,'vision_mission_values','<div class=\"award-images vision-mission-values-div\">\r\n<div class=\"award-1\">\r\n<div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/vision.png\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"award-name\">\r\n<p><strong>Vision</strong></p>\r\nEvery needy person gets excellencein eye care.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"award-1\">\r\n<div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/mission.png\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"award-name\">\r\n<p><strong>Mission</strong></p>\r\nWe are committed to quality, comprehensive eye care with equity, with education and research in eye care.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"award-1\">\r\n<div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/core-values.png\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"award-name\">\r\n<p><strong>Core Values</strong></p>\r\nHonesty, ethics, transparency, quality and commitment to cause.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"common-wrapper clear-both clear-both float-left\">\r\n<h2 class=\"common-title text-center mt-5 \">Excellence in Quality Eye Care with Concern</h2>\r\n<p>Our ‘privilege’ services include an air conditioned waiting area, the availability of personal attendants to help fast-track service delivery and a private section with a separate waiting are with good ambience. Since the past few years,our privilege services have earned the confidence of the privileged class, which is evident by the increasing number of patients at our OPD.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to our privilege services, we are known for our passion to reach out to the weaker sections of the society who are unable to afford treatment. We do not turn a single patient away. For those who cannot reach us, we reach out to them through our vision centres and outreach activities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"common-wrapper clear-both\">\r\n<h2 class=\"common-title text-center mt-5 \">State-of-the-art Facilities</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both float-left\">\r\n<p>PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital has all the latest equipment, which includes an ND:YAG laser machine, B Scan facility, Pentacam, Phaco machine, portable vitrectomy facility, Lumenis multisport laser machine, and a Mobile Eye Care van facility, to provide the highest quality of services to patients. In addition, it has a team of highly experienced specialists with years of experience. What’s more, the hospital’s skills &amp; training centre ensures that its in-house doctors are updated with all the latest techniques and knowledge related to their field.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"common-wrapper clear-both\">\r\n<h2 class=\"common-title text-center\">Our Pillars</h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Nitin R. Desai\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Nitin R. Desai\" data-designation=\"Chairman\" data-html=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Nitin R. Desai</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image