heir glasses and educating them about LASIK surgery. For those who are found to be unfit for LASIK, we provide PRK.\r\nThe availability of the latest technologically advanced diagnostic equipment and laser technology has enabled us to provide better, safer and predictable outcomes. Wavefront-guided LASIK is among the most preferred methods for vision correction worldwide. With its excellent safety profile, patient comfort and superior visual outcomes, wavefront-guided laser platforms provide the best image quality with a clearer vision. The entire vision correction procedure takes less than 15 minutes, and patients are able to resume their day-to-day activities the very next day.\r\n\r\nH.V. DESAI Eye Hospital is equipped with the best diagnostics equipment such as the pentacamHR, corneal wavefront analyser -Keratron scout and ORK wavefront analyser.\r\n\r\n','LASIK','LASIK (Laser Assisted In Situ Keratomileusis) surgery and excimer \r\nlaser photorefractive keretectomy (PRK) is the most common \r\nvision correction procedure to treat the refractive \r\nerrors of the eye all over the world.','publish','open','closed','','lasik','','','2019-07-05 11:40:34','2019-07-05 11:40:34','',0,'http://test.hvd.com/?post_type=facilities&#038;p=264',0,'facilities','',0),(265,1,'2019-05-22 09:33:00','2019-05-22 09:33:00','','HVD-at-a-Glance','','inherit','open','closed','','hvd-at-a-glance-2','','','2019-05-22 09:33:00','2019-05-22 09:33:00','',192,'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/HVD-at-a-Glance.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(266,1,'2019-05-22 09:33:05','2019-05-22 09:33:05','<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since its inception in the year 2000, PBMA’s&nbsp;H.V. Desai Eye Hospital has become a one-stop shop for vision-related treatments as well as research pertaining to advancements in the field of ophthalmology. The hospital has earned national as well as international acclaim.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Till date,&nbsp;PBMA’s&nbsp;H.V. Desai Eye Hospi