 of experienced surgeons and best technology at an affordable cost, our patients gain a spectacle free superior vision For any LASIK related queries and for fixing an appointment for consultation Contact h v desai hospital at:\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"rightSideContainer\">\r\n<div class=\"activemenu\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Lasik','','inherit','closed','closed','','264-revision-v1','','','2019-05-22 09:39:13','2019-05-22 09:39:13','',264,'http://test.hvd.com/2019/05/22/264-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(273,1,'2019-05-22 09:58:42','2019-05-22 09:58:42','<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"breadcrumbs mb-4 clear-both\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> / About Us / <strong> Board Members &amp; Trustees </strong></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"clear-both\">\n<div class=\"row mt-5\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Nitin-Desai.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Nitin R. Desai\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Nitin R. Desai\" data-designation=\"Chairman\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n		<p>He is the Chairman of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n		<p>He is the Chairman and Managing Director of M/s. Desai Brothers Ltd, Pune, a leading corporate in diversified business of food products, finance and investments, hospitality and wind power generation.</p>\n		<p>In recognition of his leading role in providing comprehensive eye care, he was felicitated by Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam, then President of India.</p>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Nitin R. Desai</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Rajesh-Shah.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Rajesh Shah\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Rajesh Shah\" data-designation=\"President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He has a family business – M/s. Jairaj & Company in Pune. </p>\n<p>He is the Senior Vice President of FAM (Federation of Association of Maharashtra), since 2003 & Vice President of FTAP (Federation of trade Associations of Pune.)</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Rajesh Shah</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Sudhir S. Sable</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Manish-Jain.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Vice President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He is the Managing Director of M/s. Kumar Properties Pvt. Ltd. which is active in the Indian Real Estate market since 1966.</p>\n<p>He is the recipient of –Enterpreneur’s  International Award for outstanding work in the field of agriculture & IMM – Top Management Club’s Award in appreciation of excellence in the field of Biotechnology.</p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Manish Jain</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row mt-5\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora\" data-designation=\"Secretary\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Hon. Secretary of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He joined the organization in the year 1986 and helped in its development and expansion. He was like a right hand man to Late Mr. N. P. Pandya and helped in raising funds for the organisation.</p>\n<p>He is the founder of Mapro Foods Pvt. Ltd., Panchagani.</p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mayur-Vora.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Mayur Vora\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Mayur Vora\" data-designation=\"Trustee\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Hon. Treasurer of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n\n<p>He is the Managing Director of Mapro Foods Pvt. Ltd., and Director in Vora Products Pvt. Ltd., as well as Purdes Radiology Pvt. Ltd.</p>\n<p>He is a member of  NFPDC, National Food Processing Development Council, Govt. of India.</p>\n<p>He is highly interested in rural education and youth activities.</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Mayur Vora</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Rahul Rathi\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Rahul Rathi\" data-designation=\"Trustee\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is a Trustee of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He is the Chairman and Fund Manager of M/s. Purnartha Investment Advisers Pvt. Ltd.</p>\n<p>He is a partner in M/s. Beharay Rathi Group of companies.</p>\n<p>He has over 15 years of research and portfolio risk management experience gained from working with global financial institutions in New York, London & Asia.</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Rahul Rathi</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circl