eir glasses and educating the people about LASIK surgery.For those unfit for LASIK we provide PRK also.\r\nCurrent technology advancements in diagnostics equipments and laser technology have enabled us with better , safer and predictable outcomes Wavefront guided LASIK is most preferred way of vision correction worldwide With its excellent safety profile, patient comfort and superior visual outcomes, wavefront guided laser platform gives best image quality with a clearer vision. The entire vision correction procedure takes less than 15 minutes in time and patients are able to resume to the day to day activities right from next day.\r\nH V DESAI eye hospital is equippd with best in diagnostics equipments like pentacamHR , corneal wavefront analyser -Keratron scout and ORK wavefront analyser\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-269 size-full\" src=\"http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/download-1.png\" alt=\"PENTACAM HR\" width=\"230\" height=\"219\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-full none\" src=\"http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-accessibility/imgs/alt-missing.png\" alt=\"This image requires alt text, but the alt text is currently blank. Either add alt text or mark the image as decorative.\" />\r\n<h1>SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-271 size-medium\" src=\"http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Lasik2-300x217.jpg\" alt=\"SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER\" width=\"300\" height=\"217\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-270 size-medium\" src=\"http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Lasik1-1-300x177.jpg\" alt=\"SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER\" width=\"300\" height=\"177\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-medium none\" src=\"http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-accessibility/imgs/alt-missing.png\" alt=\"This image requires alt text, but the alt text is currently blank. Either add alt text or mark the image as decorative.\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-medi