 best possible management for persons with low vision.','inherit','closed','closed','','119-autosave-v1','','','2019-07-05 07:23:55','2019-07-05 07:23:55','',119,'http://test.hvd.com/2019/06/25/119-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(485,1,'2019-06-25 06:06:47','2019-06-25 06:06:47','<div class=\"breadcrumbs mb-4 clear-both\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> / Our Facilities / Specialities /<strong> Low Vision</strong></div>\r\n \r\nThe clinic aims to provide the best possible management for persons with low vision.\r\n','Low Vision','The Clinic aims to provide the best possible management for persons with low vision.','inherit','closed','closed','','119-revision-v1','','','2019-06-25 06:06:47','2019-06-25 06:06:47','',119,'http://test.hvd.com/2019/06/25/119-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(486,1,'2019-07-05 11:06:56','2019-07-05 11:06:56','<div class=\"breadcrumbs mb-4 clear-both\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> / Our Facilities / Specialities /<strong> Contact Lens </strong></div>\n \nContact lens specialists at PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital evaluate and fit contact lenses that correct for near-sightedness (myopia), farsightedness (hyperopia) and astigmatism. Our optometrists can also recommend new options in soft and rigid lenses for presbyopia. Contact lenses also have therapeutic uses, due to which they are also prescribed for medical diagnosis. Some examples of the same include the prescription of contact lenses following injuries or corneal transplantation, contact lenses with an artificial iris and contact lenses for eye conditions such as keratoconus and aphakia.','Contact Lens','Contact Lens specialists at PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital evaluate and fit contact lenses tha\n                                                     ','inherit','closed','closed','','121-autosave-v1','','','2019-07-05 11:06:56','2019-07-05 11:06:56','',121,'http://test.hvd.com/2019/06/25/121-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(487,1,'2019-06-25 06:15:01','2019-06-25 06:15:01','<!-- wp:html -->\n<div