hah\" data-designation=\"President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He has a family business – M/s. Jairaj & Company in Pune. </p>\n<p>He is the Senior Vice President of FAM (Federation of Association of Maharashtra), since 2003 & Vice President of FTAP (Federation of trade Associations of Pune.)</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Rajesh Shah</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Sudhir S. Sable</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Vice President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He is the Managing Director of M/s. Kumar Properties Pvt. Ltd. which is active in the Indian Real Estate market since 1966.</p>\n<p>He is the recipient of –Enterpreneur’s  International Award for outstanding work in the field of agriculture & IMM – Top Management Club’s Award in appreciation of excellence in the field of Biotechnology.</p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Manish Jain</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row mt-5\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora\" data-designation=\"Secretary\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Hon. Secretary of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He joined the organization in the year 1986 and helped in its development and expansion. He was like a right hand man to Late Mr. N. P. Pandya and helped in raising funds for the organisation.</p>\n<p>He is the founder of Mapro Foods Pvt. Ltd., Panchagani.</p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Chandrakishor T. Vora</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Mayur Vora\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Mayur Vora\" data-designation=\"Trustee\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Hon. Treasurer of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n\n<p>He is the Managing Director of Mapro Foods Pvt. Ltd., and Director in Vora Products Pvt. Ltd., as well as Purdes Radiology Pvt. Ltd.</p>\n<p>He is a member of  NFPDC, National Food Processing Development Council, Govt. of India.</p>\n<p>He is highly interested in rural education and youth activities.</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Mayur Vora</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Rahul Rathi\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Rahul Rathi\" data-designation=\"Trustee\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is a Trustee of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He is the Chairman and Fund Manager of M/s. Purnartha Investment Advisers Pvt. Ltd.</p>\n<p>He is a partner in M/s. Beharay Rathi Group of companies.</p>\n<p>He has over 15 years of research and portfolio risk management experience gained from working with global financial institutions in New York, London & Asia.</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Rahul Rathi</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Dhanraj Patil\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Dhanraj Patil\" data-designation=\"Trustee\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Trustee of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He was appointed as Braille Instructor for the inmates of Yerewada Jail and after acquiring the skill, he helped  the inmates in writing the ‘Dnyaneshwari’ in braille language.</p>\n<p>He is the Editor of Antar Jyoti Bi-monthly Braille magazine run by The Poona Blind Men’s Association. </p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Dhanraj Patil</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!----<table class=\"wp-block-table w-100\"><tbody><tr><th>Designation</th><th>Member Name</th><th>Address</th><th>Occupation</th></tr><tr><td>CHAIRMAN</td><td>MR. NITIN R. DESAI</td><td>M/S. DESAI BROTHERS LTD.,<br>177/2, DHOLE PATIL ROAD,<br>PUNE – 411 001.</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>PRESIDENT</td><td>MR. RAJESH SHAH</td><td>1/21, ADARSHNAGAR, KANCHAN BUNGLOW,PUNE- SATARA ROAD&nbsp;<br>PUNE– 411 037.</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>VICE PRESIDENT</td><td>MR. SUDHIR S. SABLE</td><td>M/S. SABLE WAGHIRE &amp; CO.,<br>105, BHAWANI PETH, PUNE -411042</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>VICE PRESIDENT</td><td>MR. MANISH JAIN</td><td>M/S. KUMAR PROPERTIES,<br>KUMAR CAPITAL, 1ST FLOOR,<br>2413, EAST STREET, CAMP,<br>PUNE – 411 001</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>SECRETARY</td><td>MR. CHANDRAKISHOR T. VORA</td><td>1105/5, SHIVAJINAGAR,<br>HAREKRISHNA MANDIR ROAD,<br>ABOVE BANK OF MAHARASHTRA,<br>MODEL COLONY, PUNE – 411 016.</td><td>Social Worker</td></tr><tr><td>TRUSTEE</td><td>MR. MAYUR VORA</td><td>KUSHAL KUNJ, CHESSON ROAD,<br>PANCHGANI, 412805.</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>TRUSTEE</td><td>MR. RAHUL RATHI</td><td>347, SIND CO-OP,HSG SOCY.,<br>ROAD NO.3,AUNDH, GANESHKHIND, PUNE 411 007</td><td>Businessman</td></tr><tr><td>TRUSTEE</td><td>MR. DHANRAJ PATIL</td><td>SR NO 27/3, B, MUJABA VASTI NEAR GANESH TEMPLE, DHANORI,&nbsp;<br>P