me</a> / About Us / <strong> Board Members &amp; Trustees </strong></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"clear-both\">\n<div class=\"row mt-5\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Nitin-Desai.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Nitin R. Desai\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Nitin R. Desai\" data-designation=\"Chairman\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n		<p>He is the Chairman of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H.V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n		<p>He is the Chairman and Managing Director of M/s. Desai Brothers Ltd, Pune, a leading corporate in diversified business of food products, finance and investments, hospitality and wind power generation.</p>\n		<p>In recognition of his leading role in providing comprehensive eye care, he was felicitated by Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam, then President of India.</p>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Nitin R. Desai</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Rajesh-Shah.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Rajesh Shah\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Rajesh Shah\" data-designation=\"President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association and PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He has a family business – M/s. Jairaj & Company in Pune. </p>\n<p>He is the Senior Vice President of FAM (Federation of Association of Maharashtra), since 2003 & Vice President of FTAP (Federation of trade Associations of Pune.)</p></div>\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Rajesh Shah</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Sudhir S. Sable\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Sudhir S. Sable</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"common-circle data-circle\" style=\"background-position-x: -150px; background-image: url(\'http://test.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Manish-Jain.png\');\" title=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-image=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/placeholder.png\" data-name=\"Mr. Manish Jain\" data-designation=\"Vice President\" data-html=\"\">\n	<div class=\"data-html-desc\" style=\"display: none;\">\n	<p>He is the Vice President of The Poona Blind Men’s Association & PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital.</p>\n<p>He is the Managing Director of M/s. Kumar Properties Pvt. Ltd. which is active in the Indian Real Estate market since 1966.</p>\n<p>He is the recipient of –Enterpreneur’s  International Award for outstanding work in the field of agriculture & IMM – Top Management Club’s Award in appreciation of excellence in the field of Biotechnology.</p></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#bioModal\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/h-v-desai-angel-arrow.png\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pioneer-name\">Mr. Manish Jain</div>